\subsection{Datasets}
\label{s41}
To ensure complexity, we apply extensive resampling and imputation procedures to all datasets. Accordingly, the experiments are conducted on 86 time series datasets from the UCR Time Series Classification Archive \cite{UCRArchive2018} which are characterized by unequal lengths and missing values. The original train/test splits provided by the archive are discarded in favor of a single random shuffle of all data.

